<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 15:15:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国对美国芯片和车联网政策表示担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-expresses-concern-over-us-chip-connected-vehicle-policies-2024-10-08/</link><description>中国商务部长周二就美国对华半导体政策和对中国车联网的限制向美国商务部长提出“严重关切”，呼吁取消对中国企业的制裁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 14:25:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-expresses-concern-over-us-chip-connected-vehicle-policies-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok被13个州和华盛顿特区起诉，被指控伤害年轻用户</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/tiktok-sued-by-13-states-dc-accused-harming-younger-users-2024-10-08/</link><description>TikTok 周二面临美国 13 个州和哥伦比亚特区提起的新诉讼，指控这个流行的社交媒体平台伤害并未能保护年轻人。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 14:03:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/tiktok-sued-by-13-states-dc-accused-harming-younger-users-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>Arcadium 交易可能会推动力拓进入锂供应商大联盟</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/arcadium-deal-could-power-rio-tintos-entry-into-lithium-supplier-big-league-2024-10-08/</link><description>力拓 (Rio Tinto) 正在就收购锂生产商 Arcadium Lithium 进行谈判，该交易可能使这家英澳矿业公司成为第三大电动汽车电池金属生产商。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 13:44:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/arcadium-deal-could-power-rio-tintos-entry-into-lithium-supplier-big-league-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>随着顶级球队的冲突，多产的日本将目光投向沙特阿拉伯</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/prolific-japan-set-sights-saudi-arabia-top-teams-clash-2024-10-08/</link><description>周四在吉达举行的世界杯预选赛亚洲区第三轮比赛中，日本队将对阵排名第二的沙特阿拉伯队，他们希望继续他们多产的开局，因为积分榜上的交锋将成为整个非洲大陆的焦点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 13:28:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/prolific-japan-set-sights-saudi-arabia-top-teams-clash-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯将在东盟峰会上讨论缅甸、南海和乌克兰问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/blinken-discuss-myanmar-south-china-sea-ukraine-asean-summits-2024-10-08/</link><description>美国东亚事务高级外交官安东尼·布林肯将代表美国出席本周在老挝举行的东南亚国家联盟峰会，并预计将讨论缅甸的人权、中国在南海和乌克兰的“不负责任”行为周二说。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 13:25:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/blinken-discuss-myanmar-south-china-sea-ukraine-asean-summits-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>部长称在巴基斯坦遇难的中国工程师曾在一家发电厂工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-engineers-killed-pakistan-worked-power-plant-says-minister-2024-10-08/</link><description>巴基斯坦财政部长周二表示，周日在巴基斯坦卡拉奇国际机场附近发生的爆炸中丧生的两名中国公民是一家发电厂工作人员。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 13:00:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-engineers-killed-pakistan-worked-power-plant-says-minister-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>英国军情五处间谍负责人称，俄罗斯格鲁乌试图在英国和欧洲制造“混乱”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/russias-gru-seeking-cause-mayhem-britain-europe-uks-mi5-spy-chief-says-2024-10-08/</link><description>英国国内间谍负责人周二表示，俄罗斯军事情报部门正试图在英国和欧洲制造“混乱”，而来自基地组织和伊斯兰国日益增长的威胁是他最担心的恐怖主义问题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 12:13:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/russias-gru-seeking-cause-mayhem-britain-europe-uks-mi5-spy-chief-says-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>英国军情五处间谍负责人详细介绍英国面临的安全威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uks-mi5-spy-chief-details-security-threats-facing-uk-2024-10-08/</link><description>英国国内间谍负责人肯·麦卡勒姆在周二关于英国面临的威胁的年度报告中警告称，俄罗斯和伊朗构成的危险以及对基地组织和伊斯兰国日益增长的担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 12:09:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uks-mi5-spy-chief-details-security-threats-facing-uk-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪希望在印度生产汽车，但没有放宽投资规则的“直接”信号</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-wants-build-cars-india-has-no-direct-signal-investment-rules-easing-2024-10-08/</link><description>中国比亚迪高管表示，该公司希望在印度生产汽车，但尚未收到新德里关于可能放宽对中国企业严格投资规定的“直接”信号，该公司寻求在快速增长的市场扩张。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 11:33:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-wants-build-cars-india-has-no-direct-signal-investment-rules-easing-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>英国在线零售商 Shein 2023 年销售额达 20 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/online-retailer-sheins-2023-sales-hit-2-bln-uk-2024-10-08/</link><description>在线快时尚集团周二提交的一份文件显示，Shein 的英国业务 2023 年收入为 15.5 亿英镑（20 亿美元），该公司正准备在伦敦进行备受争议的上市。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 11:24:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/online-retailer-sheins-2023-sales-hit-2-bln-uk-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾和中国在最新南海争端中相互指责</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-china-trade-blame-latest-south-china-sea-spat-2024-10-08/</link><description>菲律宾指责中国海警周二向在南海争议浅滩向渔民运送补给品的政府船只发射高压水枪，但北京表示，在这些船只侵入其水域后，已采取“控制措施”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 11:09:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-china-trade-blame-latest-south-china-sea-spat-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>随着刺激乐观情绪消退，在美上市的中国公司股价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/us-listed-shares-chinese-firms-slide-stimulus-optimism-ebbs-2024-10-08/</link><description>由于投资者担心缺乏新的刺激措施来推动经济复苏，在美国上市的中国公司股票周二下跌，上海股市在经历了一周的休市后开局不佳。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 10:31:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/us-listed-shares-chinese-firms-slide-stimulus-optimism-ebbs-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>美国官员称中国锂供应过剩是为了消灭竞争对手</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-is-oversupplying-lithium-eliminate-rivals-us-official-says-2024-10-08/</link><description>一位美国高级官员在访问拥有充足锂储量的葡萄牙时表示，中国锂生产商正在向全球市场大量供应这种关键金属，并试图消除竞争项目，导致“掠夺性”价格下跌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 10:22:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-is-oversupplying-lithium-eliminate-rivals-us-official-says-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>由于投资者关注通胀数据和第三季度盈利，标普 500 指数和纳斯达克指数上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/futures-tick-higher-with-inflation-data-earnings-view-2024-10-08/</link><description>华尔街主要股指周二开盘走高，投资者将注意力转向即将到来的第三季度财报季和通胀数据，以寻求美联储未来利率决定的暗示。</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 10:18:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/futures-tick-higher-with-inflation-data-earnings-view-2024-10-08/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：股市停滞，恒生指数大幅下跌，油价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-08/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 10:15:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>